    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been meticulously maintained. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. Braking performance is handled by ventilated, cross-drilled rotors with excellent thermal management. A mechanically sound example that prioritizes driving dynamics and structural integrity.",
